                <h3>Automatic Face and Gesture Recognition 2006 </h3>
          </div>
          
          <div class="boxContent">
            <div align="left">
              <img src="http://ia360911.us.archive.org:9090/wayback/20060923233953im_/http://www.ecs.soton.ac.uk/news/Images/fg2006.gif" alt="Photo: Professor Tim Berners-Lee" width="80" height="103" hspace="5" border="1" align="left"/> 
