              International Conference on<br />
              Automatic Face and Gesture Recognition</a>. Co-chaired by our Professor <a href="http://ia360911.us.archive.org:9090/wayback/20060923233953/http://www.ecs.soton.ac.uk/people/msn">Mark Nixon</a>   with Professor Joseph Kittler from Surrey. The conference  is being attended by over 150 delegates from around the world.<br />
              <img src="http://ia360911.us.archive.org:9090/wayback/20060923233953im_/http://www.ecs.soton.ac.uk/news/Images/box1x1.gif" alt="space" width="5" height="5" style="display:block;clear:left;" />
